/* ============================================================================

   SECTION 14: ACTIVITY CARD STYLING
   ============================================================================
   Targets: Activity/Rich Presence cards in user profiles and popouts
   Purpose: Style game/app activity cards with purple theme, remove purple timestamp backgrounds
   Strategy: Multi-layer targeting (class selectors, attribute selectors, color-based detection)
   ============================================================================ */
/*
 * ORGANIZATION:
 * A. CSS Variables & Resets
 * B. Container Styling (Package 1: System UI Panel Effect)
 * C. Game/App Title (Package 1: Magical Glow)
 * D. App Icon (Package 1: Glowing Artifact)
 * E. Timestamp/Badge Removal (Purple Background Fix)
 * F. Text Elements & Visibility
 * G. Inline Style Overrides (Color-Based Detection)
 *
 * STRATEGY: Multi-layer resilience for Discord class name changes
 * - Attribute selectors [class*='partial']
 * - Context-based targeting
 * - Color-based detection (ultimate fallback)
 */

/* ----------------------------------------
   A. CSS VARIABLES & RESETS
   ---------------------------------------- */
/* Reset theme variables that might apply purple backgrounds */
[class*='activityCard'],
[class*='activityPanel'],
[class*='richPresence'] {
  --background-accent: transparent !important;
  --background-floating: transparent !important;
  --background-primary: transparent !important;
  --background-secondary: transparent !important;
  --background-tertiary: transparent !important;
  --background-modifier-hover: transparent !important;
  --background-modifier-active: transparent !important;
  --background-modifier-selected: transparent !important;
}

